#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus 3.33 LTS - new LTS version"
msgstr "Quarkus 3.33 LTS - 新的 LTS 版本"

#. type: YAML Front Matter: synopsis
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We released Quarkus 3.33 LTS, our new LTS version."
msgstr "我们发布了新的 LTS 版本 Quarkus 3.33 LTS。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "It is our pleasure to announce the release of Quarkus 3.33, which is our new LTS (Long Term Support) version."
msgstr "我们很高兴地宣布 Quarkus 3.33 正式发布，这是我们新的 LTS（长期支持）版本。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This version is built on the top of Quarkus 3.32.\n"
"New features landed in https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-34-released/[Quarkus 3.34], which was also released today."
msgstr "该版本建立在 Quarkus 3.32 的基础之上。今天发布的 link:https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-34-released/[Quarkus 3.34] 也具有新功能。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you want to know more about our LTS policy, the https://quarkus.io/blog/lts-releases/[LTS announcement] is a must read."
msgstr "如果您想进一步了解我们的 LTS 政策，请务必阅读 link:https://quarkus.io/blog/lts-releases/[LTS 公告] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "LTS releases are supported for 12 months."
msgstr "LTS 版本的支持期为 12 个月。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you are coming from the previous LTS, Quarkus 3.27 LTS, there are a lot of exciting new features and we recommend reading the following announcements:"
msgstr "如果您使用的是 Quarkus 3.27 LTS，那么我们建议您阅读以下公告："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-28-released/[Quarkus 3.28 - More security features, custom Grafana dashboards, support for multiple clients in Liquibase MongoDB, and more]"
msgstr "link:https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-28-released/[Quarkus 3.28 - 更多安全功能、自定义 Grafana 面板、支持 Liquibase MongoDB 中的多个客户端等。]"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-29-released/[Quarkus 3.29 - Multiple cache backends and Qute DAP debugger support]"
msgstr "link:https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-29-released/[Quarkus 3.29 - 支持多种缓存后端和 Qute DAP 调试器]"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-30-released/[Quarkus 3.30 - JsonView on REST Client, Hibernate Validator 9.1, CLI decrypt command, and more]"
msgstr "link:https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-30-released/[Quarkus 3.30 - REST 客户端上的 JsonView、Hibernate 验证器 9.1、CLI 解密命令等]"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-31-released/[Quarkus 3.31 - Full Java 25 support, Quarkus Maven packaging, Panache Next, and more!]"
msgstr "link:https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-31-released/[Quarkus 3.31 - 完全支持 Java 25、Quarkus Maven 打包、Panache Next 等！]"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-32-released/[Quarkus 3.32 - Project Leyden integration, more graceful shutdown, automatic Consul registration and more!]"
msgstr "link:https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-32-released/[Quarkus 3.32 - Project Leyden 集成、更优雅的关机、自动 Consul 注册等！]"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Update"
msgstr "更新"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To update to Quarkus 3.33 LTS, we recommend updating to the latest version of the Quarkus CLI and run:"
msgstr "要更新到 Quarkus 3.33 LTS，我们建议更新到最新版本的 Quarkus CLI 并运行："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Note that `quarkus update` can update your applications from any version of Quarkus (including 2.x) to Quarkus 3.33 LTS."
msgstr "请注意， `quarkus update` 可以将您的应用程序从任何版本的 Quarkus（包括 2.x）更新到 Quarkus 3.33 LTS。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you are upgrading from 3.32, there's nothing to do as 3.33 LTS is the direct continuation of 3.32."
msgstr "如果您是从 3.32 升级，那就没什么可做的了，因为 3.33 LTS 是 3.32 的直接延续。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you are upgrading from the previous LTS, Quarkus 3.27 LTS, please refer to the following migration guides:"
msgstr "如果您要从 Quarkus 3.27 LTS 升级，请参阅以下迁移指南："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.28[Migration guide for 3.28]"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.28[3.28 迁移指南]"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.29[Migration guide for 3.29]"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.29[3.29 版迁移指南]"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.30[Migration guide for 3.30]"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.30[3.30 版迁移指南]"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.31[Migration guide for 3.31]"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.31[3.31 迁移指南]"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.32[Migration guide for 3.32]"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.32[3.32 迁移指南]"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.33[Migration guide for 3.33] - this one is empty as 3.33 is the continuation of 3.32"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.33[3.33 迁移指南] --本 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.33[指南为空] ，因为 3.33 是 3.32 的延续"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-03-25-quarkus-3-33-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Note that `quarkus update` should handle most of the heavy lifting for you,\n"
"but there are still cases that should be handled manually and we recommend reading these migration guides carefully."
msgstr "请注意， `quarkus update` 可以帮你处理大部分繁重的工作，但仍有一些情况需要手动处理，我们建议你仔细阅读这些迁移指南。"

